      *----------------------------------------------------------------*        
      *    I053 - PHYSICAL INVENTORY 'MASS DELETE' ADJUSTMENTS.        *        
      *                                                                *        
      *    THIS PROGRAM IS INVOKED FROM INKCS010.                      *        
      *                                                                *        
      *    IT IS USED TO CREATE ADJUSTMENTS THAT WILL DECREASE UNITS   *        
      *    FOR RECORDS THAT EXIST ON TSUMINV/TADJADD.  THESE DECREASES *        
      *    WILL BE FOR EXISTING AREAS, AND THE ADJUSTMENT RECORD WILL  *        
      *    BE PUT IN TADJDTL.                                          *        
      *                                                                *        
      *    IT WILL ALSO CREATE ADJUSTMENTS FOR AREA '888888' WHICH IS A*        
      *    SPECIAL AREA USED BY LOSS PREVENTION TO PUT DECREASE        *        
      *    ADJUSTMENTS WHEN THE ORIGINAL AREA IS UNKNOWN.  THE AREA    *        
      *    88888888 MAY OR MAY NOT EXIST ON TSUMINV/TADJADD.           *        
      *    WHEN THE RECORDS DOES NOT EXIST ON EITHER TABLE, CREATE A   *        
      *    RECORDS IN THE TADJADD.  WHEN THE RECORDS DOES EXIST, CREATE*        
      *    A RECORD IN THE TADJDTL TABLE.                              *        
      *----------------------------------------------------------------*        
W21732*    IGSI      11/27/02  - WR21732 - NI SKU                      *00160000
W21732*    ACCEPT AND DISPLAY NON-INTELLIGENT SKU INSTEAD OF DEPT,CLASS*00160000
W21732*    AND SEQ NBR.                                                *00160000
