      **--------------------------------------------------------------**        
      ** THE CALLING PARAMETER LIST (DPWS010) FOR THE NUMERIC EDIT    **        
      ** SUB-ROUTINE (DPKUT100).                                      **        
      **--------------------------------------------------------------**        
