W26600     MOVE PV-STORE-NBR-9             TO  ADJDTL-LOC-NBR.                  
                                                                                
           MOVE ASC-AREA-NBR               TO  ADJDTL-AREA-NBR.                 
                                                                                
25248      MOVE ASC-SKU (ASC-SUB)          TO PV-UPC.                           
