                   WHEN SQLCODE > ZERO                                          
W26600                 MOVE '5220-INSERT-TADJDTL-ROW'                           
                                         TO DP013-PARAGRAPH                     
                       MOVE 'INSERT A ROW ON THE TADJADD TABLE'                 
                                         TO DP013-MESSAGE-TEXT(1)               
                       MOVE SQLCA        TO DP013-SQLCA                         
